parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the driver's seat frame can cause the seat to become unstable, rock back and forth, or even break, leading to a loss of control of the vehicle and increasing the risk of an accident.
symptoms: The driver's seat feels unstable
rocks back and forth
or makes a popping or grinding noise. The seat may also lean to one side or move independently while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rust and failure of the rear subframe can cause the vehicle to lose control, swerve, or fishtail, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle sways or fishtails while driving
the rear tires are slanted inward or outward
the vehicle shakes or vibrates
the rear subframe is rusted or broken
the control arms or sway bar are detached or broken.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to stall, jerk, or hesitate, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates or jerks when accelerating
the transmission slips or fails to engage
the vehicle stalls or loses power
unusual noises or vibrations when shifting gears.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the CVT transmission can cause the vehicle to stall, jerk, or hesitate, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates or jerks when accelerating
the transmission slips or fails to engage
the vehicle stalls or loses power
unusual noises or vibrations when shifting gears
grinding or screeching sounds from the transmission.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear differential can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle loses power or acceleration
unusual noises or vibrations from the rear of the vehicle
grinding or screeching sounds from the rear differential.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transfer case can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle loses power or acceleration
unusual noises or vibrations from the transfer case
grinding or screeching sounds from the transfer case.
